&lt;li&gt;Prospect and sell opportunities into multi-location brands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent SOCi at top industry and vertical events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a subject matter expert on the value and benefits of localized marketing at scale and how SOCi can support their needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work collaboratively with a team to drive growth with new and existing customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously stay abreast of new company technologies and services to maintain a competitive advantage&lt;/li&gt;
